    "$schema": "./sunsetted_measures.schema.json",
    "introduction": "<h3>Sunsetted/Deactivated Measures</h3>Measure versions are listed below, with three flag fields to indicate the reasons for deactivation:<ul><li><strong>TRM Update:</strong> Measures from the previous TRM that are no longer included in the new TRM.</li><li><strong>Measure Update Version:</strong> Measure version is expired. A new measure version with data updated for the latest program year is available. The latest version should be used.</li><li><strong>Measure Sunsetted or Deactivated:</strong> The entire measure package is sunsetted, or deactivated, without a replacement version for various reasons, such as code or market changes.</li></ul>Measures are grouped by the End Use category in the same manner as the Table of Contents. The \"#.#\" measure IDs refer to previous CMUA TRM measures, while \"SWXX###-##\" measure IDs are eTRM measures.",
